  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is available on Room Only and Self Catering basis.</p>
<p>There are plenty of options just a few steps from your front door in central Whistler. The Hilton Resort &amp; Spa's on site restaurant, the Cinnamon Bear Grille, is a great option serving West Coast cuisine. The nearby Cinnamon Bear Bar is a great place for an après-ski drink after hitting the slopes. </p>
<p>If you fancy dining in, grocery deliveries are also available.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
