  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studios</strong> can sleep up to two people in a King or Queen bed and have a kitchenette with mini-fridge, microwave and sink.</p>
<p><strong>Premier Studios </strong>can sleep up to four with a King bed and double sofa bed. They have a fully equipped kitchen and balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Hilton Rooms </strong>are spacious and beautifully refurbished. They can sleep up to four people with two double beds.</p>
<p><strong>Family One Bedroom Combos </strong>sleep between four and six people. They consist of a Hilton room connecting to Premier Studio forming a two-bedroom unit.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Family Combo</strong> rooms are also available on request. These consist of an interconnecting Hilton room and Studio room.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Minibar / fridge</li>
<li>Tea / coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
